  "body": "Hello Aden Team,\n\nI would like to contribute to the Hive framework by building an Email Assistant Agent integration.\n\nThis agent will help automate email-related workflows such as:\n\n- Reading incoming emails\n\n- Classifying emails based on intent\n\n- Generating intelligent replies\n\n- Automating email responses based on defined workflows\n\nI have previously worked on a LangGraph-based Email Assistant project and would like to adapt a similar agent using the Hive framework architecture.\n\nThis contribution aligns with the roadmap goals related to integrations, agent templates, and real-world business use cases.\n\nI would like to know if this contribution would be valuable and if I can be assigned to work on this integration.\n\nLooking forward to your guidance.\n\nThank you.",
